Runbook: DLP Response Actions (Mitigate + Close)
Response Menu (choose based on outcome)
1.	No Action / Informational Close
	Mark as informational and document rationale 
2.	User Education Response
	Follow up with user: explain why it was risky; point to approved workflows 
3.	Access / Exposure Reduction
	Remove or revoke access to exposed content (where applicable) 
	Apply or correct classification/labeling to prevent recurrence 
4.	Account / Endpoint Containment (High Risk)
	If evidence suggests theft/exfiltration or broader compromise, align to incident response containment actions and escalation paths (containment, disabling/rotating credentials, isolating devices, evidence handling, escalation). 
5.	Closeout
	Add notes/comments, update status to resolved, assign ownership if needed 
